## 3. Buttons

| Type | Style | Example |
|------|-------|---------|
| **Selection** (teams, weekdays, slots) | Blue: `bg-blue-600 text-white` when selected, `bg-gray-100 text-gray-700` when idle | Team pickers, slot toggles |
| **Action** (Save, Cancel, Add, Delete) | Semantic variants | `variant="outline"` Cancel, `variant="destructive"` Delete |

```tsx
// ✅ Selection buttons (blue)
<Button className={cn(
  isSelected ? 'bg-blue-600 text-white' : 'bg-gray-100 text-gray-700'
)}>
  {team}
</Button>

// ✅ Action buttons (semantic)
<Button type="submit">Save</Button>
<Button variant="outline" onClick={onCancel}>Cancel</Button>
<Button variant="destructive" onClick={handleDelete}>Delete</Button>
```

