## 7. Cards & Content Grouping

Cards are for **self-contained, modular units**—not for wrapping every sub-element.

| Use Card For | Don't Use Card For |
|--------------|-------------------|
| Dashboard widgets | Individual form rows |
| Team/entity summaries | Inline metadata pairs |
| Configurable panels | Static text blocks |

Prefer **section headers with spacing** over nested cards:

```tsx
// ✅ Section with header + grid
<div className="space-y-3">
  <div className="flex items-center justify-between">
    <h3 className="text-sm font-medium">Active Merges</h3>
    <Button size="sm">Create Merge</Button>
  </div>
  <div className="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
    {/* Flat cards, not nested */}
  </div>
</div>
```

