## Summary Checklist

When creating new UI components:

- [ ] **Structure**: Flat hierarchy (max 2 nesting levels), use spacing/dividers not nested borders
- [ ] **Progressive disclosure**: Show essential info inline, hide complexity behind expand/collapse
- [ ] **Icons**: lucide-react only (no emojis)
- [ ] **Buttons**: Selection = blue, Actions = semantic variants
- [ ] **Dropdowns**: Radix `Select` components (not native `<select>`)
- [ ] **Dialogs**: `max-w-lg` default, wider only for tables/forms
- [ ] **Tooltips**: White background with border
- [ ] **Cards**: Use for modular units, not for every sub-element
